title: Very fetching: dachshund fashion show opens NGV Kids Summer festival – video
text:
Dogs Very fetching: dachshund fashion show opens NGV Kids Summer festival – video 
The National Gallery of Victoria Kids Summer festival in Melbourne opened on Monday with dachshunds strutting the catwalk. An audience of children and pup-arazzi looked on as the dogs paraded outfits inspired by current NGV exhibitions David Hockney: Current and Viktor&Rolf: Fashion Artists. 
• The NGV Kids Summer Festival runs from 16 to 26 January Source: National Gallery of Victoria Monday 16 January 2017 23.09 GMT View more sharing options
